ISLAMABAD, Aug 1 (APP): The Spokesperson Ministry of Power while contradicting news item aired on a private channel about data of demand and supply on Monday clarified more electricity is available in the system as compared to the demand.
In a statement, the Spokesperson said there is no shortage of the electricity in the country adding that current the generation stood at 19,500 MW.
